<div class="comment" id="comment-47755823">
  <div class="comment_head"><a href="/user/jagged-chisel">jagged-chisel</a> 1 day ago</div>
  <div class="comment_text">&quot;Alignment&quot;<p>In what world would I ever expect a commercial (or governmental) entity to have precise alignment with me personally, or even with my own business? I argue those relationships are necessarily adversarial, and trusting anyone else to align their &quot;AI&quot; tool to my goals, needs, and&#x2F;or desires is a recipe for having my livelihood completely reassigned into someone else&#x27;s wallet.</div>
